OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1772471475
OL,3,CFifth man charged with murder of
OL,4,CSuhail Choudry in Keighley
OL,6,FA 42-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith the murder of a 35-year-old
OL,8,Ffather of two who died following a
OL,9,Fserious assault in Keighley.
OL,11,FSuhail Choudry was found with serious
OL,12,Fhead injuries in Flasby Street in the
OL,13,Fearly hours of Sunday, 8 February.
OL,15,FHe was taken to hospital where he died
OL,16,Fthree days later.
OL,18,FMajid Hussain, of Devonshire Street,
OL,19,FKeighley was charged with murder,
OL,20,Fpossession of an offensive weapon in a
OL,21,Fpublic place, and violent disorder.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
