PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1772471475
OL,3,CFifth man charged with murder of
OL,4,CSuhail Choudry in Keighley
OL,6,FHussain, remains in custody and will
OL,7,Fappear at Bradford Magistrates Court
OL,8,Fon Monday.
OL,10,FFour other men have already been
OL,11,Fcharged with murder.
OL,13,FRashid Hussain, 41, of Redcliffe
OL,14,FStreet, Mohammed Aliyan Khan, 23,
OL,15,FFaisal Khan, 26, both of Malsis Road,
OL,16,Fand Hakeem Gulzar, 27, of Plover
OL,17,FStreet, have all been charged with
OL,18,Fmurder, possession of an offensive
OL,19,Fweapon in a public place and violent
OL,20,Fdisorder.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
