PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1772471475
OL,3,CFifth man charged with murder of
OL,4,CSuhail Choudry in Keighley
OL,6,FA 27-year-old man and a 34-year-old
OL,7,Fwoman were also arrested on Saturday
OL,8,Fafternoon or assisting an offender in
OL,9,Frelation to the investigation.
OL,11,FWest Yorkshire Police said initial
OL,12,Fenquiries have shown Mr Choudry had
OL,13,Fbeen chased and assaulted by a group,
OL,14,Farmed with weapons such as bats and
OL,15,Fsticks.
OL,17,FTwo other men, aged 21 and 24, were
OL,18,Falso assaulted during the incident but
OL,19,Ftheir injuries were not serious or
OL,20,Flife threatening.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
