PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1772471475
OL,3,CFifth man charged with murder of
OL,4,CSuhail Choudry in Keighley
OL,6,FIn a tribute to her husband, Zara
OL,7,FChoudry, who is pregnant with their
OL,8,Fthird child, described him as "a
OL,9,Ffather before anything" adding that it
OL,10,Fwas "his proudest title and he was
OL,11,Ftheir world".
OL,13,FShe added: "Telling our children their
OL,14,Fdaddy has passed away is something no
OL,15,Fmother should have to do, we will
OL,16,Fnever find peace with the brutality in
OL,17,Fwhich he left us."
OL,26,@uD@LOU
